*&quot;Premier Eleven&quot; (Sammy/Dimps, 2003)
*&quot;Chase 1929&quot; (Sammy, 2004)
*&quot;Force Five&quot; (Sammy, 2004)
*&quot;Kenju&quot; (Sammy / DreamFactory, 2004)

